  "prompt": "Why did my guy friend ask me if I have a boyfriend or not?",
  "response": "There could be several reasons why your guy friend asked if you have a boyfriend. Here are a few possibilities:\n\n1. **Interest in You**: He might be interested in you romantically and wants to know if you\u2019re available.\n\n2. **Curiosity**: He may simply be curious about your relationship status for friendship reasons or to understand your life situation better.\n\n3. **Concern for You**: If he knows you\u2019ve gone through a tough time in your love life, he might be checking in to see how you\u2019re doing.\n\n4. **Casual Conversation**: It could also just be a casual question that came up in conversation without any deeper intent.\n\n5. **Social Context**: He might be trying to gauge the dynamics of your friend group or social activities.\n\nUnderstanding the context and tone of the conversation can help clarify his intentions.",
